struct.exostring: M4 unit joins party. As soon as the PC leaves Janice's shop the M4 unit will explode and set the global Tar_JaniceDro to 15.

Dialog mission statement
Janice is a store that will also answer some basic questions. If the player has not purchased a droid from her she will sell them one through dialog.
If the player buys T3 the droid joins the party. If the player buys the M4 it will join the party but will explode as soon as it leaves the shop. The player can come back and get a refund or a special deal on the T3.
Only the start store exit point requires any special scripting. All other exit points do not.
The area just outside the store has to have a trigger to make the M4 blow up if the player has purchased it (Tar_JaniceDro ==20) and then set the variable back to 15
